data.description: Check out this sprawling brick home in the coveted neighborhood of North Shore Country Club. This home has an eat-in dining area adjacent to the kitchen plus gorgeous formal dining room.   Three bedrooms on the main floor with a flex space at the top of the stairs.  Family room is cozy with the fireplace and see through built-ins that bring the natural light from the other rooms. The master bathroom has a jetted tub and walk-in shower. Master suite boasts his and her closets. This home is bringing the outdoors indoors with a gorgeous sunroom.  Enjoy your outdoor living space with screened in porch and deck overlooking your inground swimming pool. An added bonus of this beautiful home is plenty of space to park with a 3 car garage!
